{"tid":1407671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[人手置頂] 連馬會 CEO 應嘉栢不反對同事 5/8 罷工","createTime":"2019-08-04T15:48:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T17:58:39.000Z","uid":276844,"like":220,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"2d99dcb0cb39eedd617679b02fb9ddc2fac238c1","tid":1407671,"uid":276844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:48:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">FACT CHECKED</span></span><br />\n<br />\n英文<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/80JQYzL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F80JQYzL.png&h=8a0f6575&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kdcin5C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKdcin5C.png&h=9027a207&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中文<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Et9uHq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Et9uHq.png&h=3e8d4ece&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n封信嘅重點<br />\n<blockquote><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">//I therefore respect the decision of those colleagues who have chosen to take part in the strike tomorrow (5 August) as they feel strongly to express their views in this manner.//</span></span></strong></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nTL;DR<br />\n<br />\n1. 我關心香港現時社會的情況<br />\n<br />\n2. 際此艱難時刻我們應保持團結，互相尊重<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3. 絕對尊重同事發表自己意見的自由，及他們於明日罷工的決定。選擇不罷工的同事亦應被尊重</span><br />\n<br />\n4. 在未來數星期將會有質疑的聲音，我們要保持團結，互相信任尊重，為社會改進作岀貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不自由，毋寧死。連馬會咁藍既公司都不反對，大家一定要多呼予自己同事一齊罷工，一支竹仔斷折彎，幾支竹一紮斷折難。祝各位萬事小心，一切順利。</span></span>"},{"pid":"c19bdaeebe69f095268fab1dda3ec4e90665f67f","tid":1407671,"uid":139882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:49:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a2778460960b048a2e6c59bc3d27c0c7367434a2","tid":1407671,"uid":276844,"like":0,"dislike":0,